      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOCHINVAR MAGIC (3) recorded another strong performance last time when he came from the back row for third at this circuit and distance, adding to a series of wins and placings. Led to win from this barrier here two back so is much better served by this draw. HEEZ A VIBE (8) produced a good effort at his latest appearance, scoring by 2 metres over this distance to take his record at this venue to five from nine. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. Go well again. HEZ ALL ROCK (1) has been racing at Melton where he finished runner-up fresh before working last start. Has switched yards since and is aided by the inside draw. DON ARTHUR (2) led to win here earlier in the month so will enjoy this draw having come from wider to place in his last two starts.",
